title: Star Trek - The Genesis Affair
description:
Since the three movies Star Trek: Wrath of Khan, The Search for Spock, and The Voyage Home are all part of the same story arc, I've cut them together into a single 5-hour+ movie. I'm not skilled enough with video editing to have altered the opening credits (they still say "The Wrath of Khan"). Maybe someone else out there can do that, and re-up an improved version.

I did the same thing for Back to the Future, here:
<https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/11281467/Back_to_the_Future_-_The_Movie>

Let me know what you think.

And please seed!

Thanx
